  "notes": "Route 38 is a short east-west route connecting Route 39 (west) to Ecruteak City (east). The main feature is the Ecruteak Gate building at the eastern end, which leads into Ecruteak City. The route has significant tall grass patches north and south of the central path. Six trainers are present: Schoolboy Chad and Lass Dana both offer phone rematches with scaling difficulty. A fruit tree yields a daily Berry. The route sign confirms the OLIVINE CITY - ECRUTEAK CITY corridor. Beauty Olivia references Moomoo Milk, tying flavor text to Route 39. The trainer Toby (Bird Keeper) heads to Cianwood to train his birds to Fly."
